source.name: ISTHA - Coordinates for Mileposts on the Illinois Tollway, I-88
source.description: This dataset has a record for every milepost on I-88 of the Illinois Tollway that includes the route number, the milepost and the latitude and longitude. It lists a milepost every tenth of mile, and every quarter of a mile, but there is actually only a physical milepost every quarter of a mile.
